## 1 Carat Emerald Cut Diamond Ring Price

A 1ct emerald cut diamond ring starts at $3,830 in natural and $2,919 in lab when you build from the cheapest certified stone plus the cheapest setting. But the natural price range at 1ct is wider than buyers expect.

Five GIA-certified natural 1ct emerald cuts are available in current certified market inventory. The range runs from [$3,140](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29333987?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) for D-VS1 to [$6,820](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/15813404?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) for E-VS1, and this is all for stones at or near exactly 1ct. The same carat weight with different color and clarity grades produces a $3,680 spread.

