[![Lab emerald cut diamond ring in rose gold — showing larger stone for same budget](https://ion.bluenile.com/sets/Jewelry/Photoshoot/Bluenile/BrioPackshotBox/Rings/505132/505132_M1_EMR_DIM_wht_0100CT_R_Box4_004_1600X1600.jpg)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings?MetalType=all&Diamonds=Dia&ShapeID=Emerald&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)

