## Final Verdict: Best 1ct Emerald Cut Diamond Ring

**Best for natural origin at minimum cost**: [GIA 1.00ct D-VS1 at $3,140](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29333987?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) + [$690 petite solitaire](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/rings/petite-emerald-cut-solitaire-diamond-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-by-james-allen-item-311196?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) = **$3,830 complete**. The right setting for the shape, the correct grades for the step-cut facets, no overpaying on invisible grade increments.

**Best for active lifestyle (natural)**: [GIA 1.00ct D-VS1 at $3,140](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29333987?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) + [$990 comfort fit bezel](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/comfort-fit-bezel-set-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-315709?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) = **$4,130 complete**. Full corner protection, daily wear without worry, clean minimal look.

**Best value overall (lab)**: [IGI 1.94ct F-VVS1 at $2,229](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29147824?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) + [$690 petite solitaire](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/rings/petite-emerald-cut-solitaire-diamond-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-by-james-allen-item-311196?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) = **$2,919 complete**. Nearly 2ct stone, VVS1 clarity, F color, for $900 less than the cheapest natural 1ct ring.

**Best for maximum lab presence**: [IGI 2.00ct D-FL at $4,735](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28828463?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) + [$1,325 micropavé](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-micropave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-10-ct-tw-item-195402?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) = **$6,060 complete**. D-FL at 2ct, the fully developed hall-of-mirrors on a 9mm × 7mm stone, with a pavé band that adds presence without the price of natural.

